  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/8a292e5674e8c6e5e373f034c23b8903.avif?t=1705809586\" width=480 height=83 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Current List</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/820b6d055b0151f114301cc6e81cb4cd.avif?t=1705809586\" width=560 height=336 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Animated On Your Desktop</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/79ef861ee3888cc87a95321e773c968a.poster.avif?t=1705809586\" width=260 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/79ef861ee3888cc87a95321e773c968a.webm?t=1705809586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/79ef861ee3888cc87a95321e773c968a.mp4?t=1705809586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>A virtual pet, companion, or other digital friend that lives on your desktop as you work, play or relax at your computer.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>They can be as big or as small as you want them to be</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>You can change how fast they animate</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Customize your pet with over 256 colors!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/0750b2ff4ccfebedc795bfae861c894e.avif?t=1705809586\" width=534 height=148 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Interact</h2>Want them in a different spot? They can be picked up and moved around your screen.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/ce908ee495e5d025ef2b2aaa6aec2bd4.poster.avif?t=1705809586\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/ce908ee495e5d025ef2b2aaa6aec2bd4.webm?t=1705809586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/ce908ee495e5d025ef2b2aaa6aec2bd4.mp4?t=1705809586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Name Them</h2>Give each of them a unique name.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/ae134ead0a018147a1b876e0b05d2d74.poster.avif?t=1705809586\" width=392 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/ae134ead0a018147a1b876e0b05d2d74.webm?t=1705809586\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/ae134ead0a018147a1b876e0b05d2d74.mp4?t=1705809586\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create Anything</h2>Create entirely new virtual pets, companions, or whatever you wish, by using any PNG image. You can add as many animations as you want to your creations.<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>PNG images can be any size</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Each animation can have its own movement speed</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/ac0de803d647b524c965698e36d9e322.avif?t=1705809586\" width=616 height=720 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2667350/extras/d5097df6cbb2afda8a995ee4d5ab1763.avif?t=1705809586\" width=600 height=1200 /></span>",
